<head><title>Admin Web Simple Guide</title>
<style>
  body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; line-height: 1.8; color: #333; font-size: 14pt; }
  h1 { color: #1a237e; border-bottom: 4px solid #7B57E4; padding-bottom: 10px; font-size: 26pt; font-weight: bold; }
  h2 { color: #7B57E4; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 22pt; background-color: #f3efff; padding: 10px; border-radius: 8px; }
